      Hard Disk is similar to the bottle neck    
     
      
      
                    if 10 GB  of the data   is loaded in RAM  and the 1GB is loaded further     the 1GB  will be on wait   if  the initial 10 GB  is not loaded 
                                  completely in   RAM
                                  
                                  
                                  
